name: Wale Vs Sharc: The Interactive Software Title For Your Computer Box
name_original: Wale Vs Sharc: The Interactive Software Title For Your Computer Box
description: Wale Vs Sharc: The Interactive Software Title For Your Computer Box (WVS:TISTFYCB for short) is a simple, light hearted text adventure based on characters and stories from the non-award winning web comic, Daingercomics. The hilarious puzzle solving antics of one Sharc and Wale are sure to delight and amaze persons of all ages. Enjoy!
